{"tid":1401430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線冇鬼但又自願比人拉唔係勇，係on9","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:24:30.000Z","uid":177213,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb94409746a2b2dcadca9a623b30678cc46fe20","tid":1401430,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">小弟自6.12之後起一直係前線玩家<br />\n<br />\n作為前線，我最撚憎連登冷氣軍師叫人撤</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但今日我玩完紅隧就主動撤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為我哋目標係撚狗啊屌你老母<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">守住個Road Block有閪用呀？<br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足你哋啲Water Be撚咗去邊呀</span><br />\n攻又唔係攻，退又唔係退都唔做乜撚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想分化<br />\n只係希望你哋可以汲取經驗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋係絕對唔會夠軍隊打<br />\n要智取啊各位</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">求各位唔好再去再守Road Block啦<br />\n我哋已經失去夠多手足喇<br />\n可唔可以真係做到伸縮自如啊咁多位</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3478c7dd237750c1dd3424d26838db3a888f18c2","tid":1401430,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BE WATER</span>"},{"pid":"458e98ad3030aa794a40d411582e01483bc6ace1","tid":1401430,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"85一齊出仲好啦, 幫人被罷工仲好啦<br />\n今日戀戰都唔知有乜用"},{"pid":"124de22dcb70e7513cf7b490f8fca32449e9f214","tid":1401430,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Hit And Run</span>"},{"pid":"66ecf1dc81a06b02972